---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Daycare Enrollment Strategies | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Master your daycare enrollment strategy by optimizing waitlists and capacity management for your specific center."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
        <!-- 1. OWNERSHIP FRAMING -->
        <section class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                YOUR enrollment strategy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Keeping your center full is an active process of managing
                relationships and timing, not just a passive result of having a
                website.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. FACTORS THAT AFFECT OUTCOME -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                What Affects Your Capacity
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Your ability to maintain full enrollment is dictated by
                effective waitlist management, understanding your churn rates,
                and optimizing your licensed capacity. Balancing age groups and
                transitions is key to maximizing revenue without violating
                regulations.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. WHY GENERIC ADVICE FAILS -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                General enrollment tips often miss the operational complexity of
                managing "aging up" and spot availability. Your strategy needs
                to align with your specific licensing capacity and the seasonal
                demand patterns of your local area.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. CTA TO CALCULATOR -->
        <section
            class="text-center py-12 px-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                See How Much YOU Could Make in Your State
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's
                regulations to see the revenue impact of full enrollment.
            </p>
            <a
                href="/tools/income-builder"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 shadow-lg transition-all"
            >
                Use the Free Calculator →
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
